{"tid":1832693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣淪陷！疾管署：國內出現首例武漢肺炎確診病例","createTime":"2020-01-21T10:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T12:17:45.000Z","uid":97944,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3486ba2ef6389d6a95b2e0593d5d0afa8d00a892","tid":1832693,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"因應「中國武漢肺炎疫情」，中央流行疫情指揮中心六時舉行記者會，說明檢驗結果，結果國內確定已出現第一例境外移入，也是國內首例武漢肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心今日公布我國確診首例境外移入嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎個案，為居住南部50多歲女性，於中國大陸武漢工作，昨日由武漢搭機入境，因有發燒、咳嗽、呼吸急促等症狀，由機場檢疫人員安排後送就醫，X光檢查顯示有肺炎，今日檢驗確認為新型冠狀病毒陽性，持續於醫院負壓隔離病房治療中。由於本個案於下飛機後立即送往醫院隔離病房治療，並未進入社區，請民眾不必恐慌。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/120936/4301137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F120936%2F4301137&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6oRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=5d3892c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/120936/4301137</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合新聞網"},{"pid":"3f7458f817a845987aca9abd6e3063d50661bee5","tid":1832693,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed97dfd4d8248b3876f76da4d9283b590de53b79","tid":1832693,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"支那人真係好仆街<br />\n將啲疫症帶埋去台灣"},{"pid":"edb086b3cac1ad7488f2733858999d96249de16c","tid":1832693,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6e8c3488948a58a5